         qr/Child tables:\s*`bug_1315130_a`\.`child_table_in_same_schema` \(approx\. 1 rows\)\s*`bug_1315130_b`\.`child_table_in_second_schema` \(approx\. 1 rows\)[^`]*?Will/s,
